title: Phil Collins - Demos 1980-1990 (1990)
description:
Phil Collins - Demos 1980-1990 (1990)

Bootleg album found on the web and sharing it with you........

Due to the 'Demo qualification' you can expect songs that are barely Finished! It are mostly 'guiding Songs' that later became songs on the albums. sometimes not even song yet....

On the CD:

01. In the Air Tonight 
02. I Missed Again
03. If Leaving me is Easy
04. Do You Know Do You Care
05. Tomorrow Never Knows (The Beatles)
06. Do You Remember
07. Something Happened on the Way to Heaven
08. All of My Life
09. Only Your Love (Genesis/Phil Collins)
